Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
The Public’s Radio is 89.3FM (WNPN) across Rhode Island and the South Coast of Massachusetts. You can use this Skill to listen to our most recent local newscast.

Once you’ve installed the Skill, say “Alexa, what’s my Flash Briefing,” or “Alexa, what’s the news.”
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
